name: Leaves Tee (Grey/Black)
description:
"...and the leaves of the tree [of life] were for the healing of the nations."

Black print on heather grey, Next Level Apparel T-shirt. Water-based ink provides the softest, almost not there print. 

A portion of each shirt goes to creating healthy, sustaining communities through Beyond Poverty.

Beyond poverty is an organization focused on holistic community development. For more information on Beyond Poeverty and what they are doing, check out their website.

http://www.beyondpoverty.org/kenya/

name: Tilapia Print
description:
Tilapia are growing rapidly as a commodity in Kenya, they produce a lot of food, are a great protein and oil source, are inexpensive to raise and are easily tended.

Two color screen print.
8.5x11 on Linux White

A portion of the funds raised from this limited edition print will be donated to our partner non-profit Beyond Poverty to help build a tilapia farm and train residents to keep it in a rural Kenyan village.

Beyond poverty is an organization focused on holistic community development. For more information on Beyond Poeverty and what they are doing, check out their website.

http://www.beyondpoverty.org/kenya/
